---
title: Zesty Tofu Bowls with Lime Aioli
description: Peppers, zucchini and tofu are a match made in heaven! This dish capitalizes on this classic trio, with crispy roasted potatoes and a creamy lime aioli to top it all off. Altogether, it's the perfect bright and punchy bowl!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220411_R1024_W22_CA_RB153688-3_KB_Main_low-34554328.jpg
